<s> Hi, There is a problem but not really a bug with shortcuts.  </s>
<s> Widows system menu associated with any application has the priority for shortcuts in form of Alt [+ character].  </s>
<s> For example, if you press only the Alt key, the File Menu will be automatically activated.  </s>
<s> To avoid that, we have to "disable" the shortcuts automatically associated with the system menu.  </s>
<s> This needs a lot of work an I prefer to do that in the next release to avoid introducing new bugs in the public release we plan to do.  </s>
<s> Anyway, the shorcuts for Zoom in is the combination of [Alt] and [+] (Where [x] represents the key x).  </s>
<s> In other terms its [Alt]+[Shift]+[+/=].  </s>
<s> The shortcut for Zoom out is: [Alt]+[-].  </s>
<s> And they works if you click into the edit Window.  </s>
