<s> This will be fixed soon.  </s>
<s> On Windows, shortcuts are introduced in something called accelerator table.  </s>
<s> This used to be done in a resource file (fortunately, it is not the case for Amaya and this is the reason why you can "dynamically" configure your shortcuts.  </s>
<s> I even can say that the only application on Windows allowing to do this is Amaya).  </s>
<s> The structure of the accelerator table does not allow to combine a sequence "a la emacs" such as Ctrl Key l, Ctrl Key d.  </s>
<s> This is the main reason which lead me to create a particular amaya.kb  </s>
<s> file for Windows.  </s>
